                    <div class="header-right">
                        <div class="category">Choosing an AI Customer Support Chatbot </div>
                        <h1 class="title"> How Much Are You Saving with Customate? </h1>
                        <div class="date">Last update: May 2025</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="article-content">

                <h2 style="margin-top: 70px;"> How Much Are You Saving with Customate? </h2>

                <p> Customer support costs vary widely depending on the business, industry, and location. To establish a baseline, we analyzed the average cost per written or spoken message handled by a human agent in a call or business center. In India, the cost per message is around €0.10, in Latin America, it’s about €0.30, and in Western and Northern Europe, it reaches approximately €1.00. In contrast, a message processed by a Customate chatbot costs only between €0.02 and €0.006, depending on the plan and volume. Even if you're operating in the lowest-cost region, that’s an immediate huge reduction in cost, and the savings only increase in higher-cost markets.  </p>

                <p>
                If you’re already using a chatbot, you might still be spending more than necessary.  <a href="https://www.customate.ai/blog/aiwins" target="_blank">Many chatbot solutions are inefficient</a>, 
                failing to resolve issues completely. When that happens, a human agent still has to step in, which means additional costs 
                in the form of lost productivity or an unnecessarily large staff. Some businesses try to minimize costs by reducing customer interactions altogether, but this approach often backfires. Unanswered questions, unresolved complaints, and a lack of engagement can lead to dissatisfied customers, lost sales, and missed opportunities to improve your product or service. </p>

                <h2 style="margin-top: 80px;"> How Does Customate Compare with Its AI-Powered Customer Support Peers? </h2>

                <p> The biggest competitor charges $1 per resolution. That makes it the best alternative only if every conversation consists of at least 100 AI-Bot messages, which is unrealistic. On average, a resolution only takes five responses, meaning you’d be overpaying. </p>

                <p> Customate offers a better price and better responses. Unlike others, we don’t charge extra for user seats or additional chatbots. You only pay for what you actually need. <a href="https://www.customate.ai/pricing" target="_blank">Click here</a> to learn more. </p>


                <h2 style="margin-top: 80px;"> Spending cuts are only the first half of the equation. </h2>

                <p> When considering a Customate subscription, you shouldn’t just focus on the costs you’ll save, but also on the earnings you can generate. </p>

                <p> Customate helps shorten sales cycles, increase customer satisfaction, and free up staff to focus on more productive tasks. It also contributes to building operational automation know-how while providing valuable insights into product quality, sales processes, and other useful feedback directly from customers. </p>

                <p> Finally, the longer you use Customate, the better it gets. Our product is constantly expanding and improving, and your bot quickly adapts to new policies and operational changes, making it an increasingly powerful tool for your business. </p>
                
